_sText:
Welcome to bhop_superdooperhard. This is the hardest ever bhop map. If you can finish this you are pro!!!!!!

This map is made for all the pro bhoppers out there like myself. If you cannot get 1000 velocity this map isnt for you. Go play bhop_eazy or something if you cant do this.

Play this map on 100 tick and 100 air accelerations.

Thanks to the creators of bhop_exodus and bhop_badges and bhop_addict_v2 for ideas i used in this map.
